        "| **LightGBM** | **96.1%** |\n",
        "\n",
        "LightGBM consistently outperformed all alternatives due to its leaf-wise tree\n",
        "growth, which produces more expressive trees per iteration within the same\n",
        "`num_leaves` budget. I selected LightGBM as the primary model for all final\n",
        "submissions.\n",
        "\n",
        "## 4.3 Number of Temporal Segments\n"
      ],
