        "| run30 | 0.7289 | 0.7893 | +0.060 |\n",
        "\n",
        "This stability confirmed that my GroupKFold CV (grouped by user) is an accurate\n",
        "proxy for generalisation to unseen users, allowing me to trust the OOF score as\n",
        "a reliable signal for model selection.\n",
