        "| Feature set | 716 hand-crafted | Axis stats + temporal segments + FFT + windows |\n",
        "| Model | LightGBM ensemble | Best CV accuracy; handles imbalance via sample weights |\n",
        "| Imbalance handling | Balanced weights + threshold opt. | Macro-F1 objective; C2, C4, C5 severely underrepresented |\n",
